{"tid":1092273,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"跌20%，你會買返本來心水單位，定再去搵更好？","createTime":"2019-04-04T16:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T02:34:55.000Z","uid":85223,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc1384deefb2f7d1b341452939e2f58dc0f0bb9","tid":1092273,"uid":85223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:36:46.000Z","msg":"現價嚟講<br />\n好多人都會有心水單位<br />\n可能而家有d貴買唔到<br />\n但如果呢刻個市跌20%<br />\n你會買返心水單位定再去搵d更好？<br />\n還是執d平貨？揀間本來負擔到，而家買完仲有錢淨"},{"pid":"079815f6ec46d4ea4ff470765c53f1692dff0bbf","tid":1092273,"uid":52595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"863e9cb0a82b2a3e2ff09f75fa1d34098ae63822","tid":1092273,"uid":40207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"更係等跌到得20%先買<br />\n唔係調整 係爆破呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10304c3042e417ca038126b45f4d15dd2b6bff04","tid":1092273,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:15:42.000Z","msg":"跌20%先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a2f630a266fc6bea97da98901b3ec22b23326b","tid":1092273,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"人既貪婪性人定搵更好，但更好既又變左買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8590d641ad1a0f78ac2f43e083d36d574e79cde3","tid":1092273,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"跌20%即係經濟差，啲人就會諗跌多10%，即係經濟更差，驚連工都無埋，最後都係睇定啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbae94b16ac31f95f0fa7c4399f8bd87d13c07ac","tid":1092273,"uid":166387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"跌20%你邊會買丫 <br />\n一定想佢再跌